Overview test The Desk is your private space and your favorite place. Here you can find a set of utilities and widgets all for you.
{{&lt; img-center src=&ldquo;/uploads/2020/04/02/desk.png&rdquo; &gt;}}
Activities This box collects all the items that were assigned to you in any [boards]({{&lt; relref &ldquo;pipeline/index.md#boards&rdquo; &gt;}}). You can scroll through them, search by item name and mark them as completed without going to the dedicated page. If this box is empty try to add a column &ldquo;Member&rdquo; in a board and set yourself as &ldquo;Activity&rsquo;s assignee&rdquo;
